When a new feature is discussed:
1) Draft a Feature Spec (FS) under docs/specs using @Spec-Template.
2) Ask at most 3 essential questions only if blocking.
3) After "accept", create a concise Patch Plan and implement with minimal diffs.
4) Update tests and link FS in the PR.
